source.name: Individuals with Disabilities Education Act (IDEA) Data - Part C: Early Intervention for Infants and Toddlers
source.description: This website provides public access to state-level data about infants and  toddlers with disabilities (ages 0 - 3) served under the Individuals with Disabilities Education Act (IDEA) - Part C; technical assistance (TA) materials to support the collection, analysis and reporting of IDEA data; and the forms and spreadsheets used for collection.
